# Terraform
**/.terraform/*
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
crash.log
crash.*.log
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json
.terraformrc
terraform.rc
plan.txt
tfplan

# Provider lock files ARE committed (pin versions) — do not ignore .terraform.lock.hcl

# tfvars may hold environment config — commit only the example template
*.tfvars
*.tfvars.json
!*.tfvars.example

# Secrets / local env
.env
*.pem
*.key
